<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Farmix</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2ecc71;
            --secondary-color: #f1c40f;
            --dark-color: #2c3e50;
            --light-color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .navbar {
            padding: 15px 0;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color) !important;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--dark-color) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0 12px;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        /* About Header */
        .about-header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)),
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1489&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-header p {
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* About Content */
        .about-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .about-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .about-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .about-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-card h3 {
            color: var(--dark-color);
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .about-card p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Team Section */
        .team-section {
            background-color: var(--light-color);
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .team-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .team-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .team-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .team-info {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .team-info h4 {
            color: var(--dark-color);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .team-info p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats-section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Farmix</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/shop">Shop</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/about">About</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                    <% if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link btn btn-login mx-2" href="/login">Login</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link btn btn-register" href="/register">Register</a>
                        </li>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link btn btn-login" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- About Header -->
    <section class="about-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Farmix</h1>
            <p>Connecting farmers and buyers for a sustainable agricultural future</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                        <p>At Farmix, we're committed to revolutionizing the agricultural marketplace by creating direct connections between farmers and buyers. Our platform empowers farmers with fair prices and provides buyers with access to fresh, quality produce.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                        <p>We envision a future where technology bridges the gap between agricultural producers and consumers, creating a transparent, efficient, and sustainable food supply chain that benefits everyone involved.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="stats-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">1000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Registered Farmers</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">5000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Active Buyers</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">10K+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Products Listed</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Districts Covered</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Trust & Transparency</h3>
                        <p>We believe in creating transparent relationships between farmers and buyers, ensuring fair prices and quality products.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                        <p>Our platform promotes sustainable farming practices and environmentally conscious distribution methods.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Community First</h3>
                        <p>We prioritize building strong agricultural communities and supporting local farmers and businesses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-dark text-light py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>About Farmix</h5>
                    <p>Your trusted agricultural marketplace connecting farmers and buyers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>Quick Links</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><a href="/" class="text-light">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/shop" class="text-light">Shop</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/services" class="text-light">Services</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/about" class="text-light">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/contact" class="text-light">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>Contact Us</h5>
                    <p>Email: info@farmix.com<br>
                    Phone: +1 234 567 890</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Farmix. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 